modName: Enb me not. Extreme Sweet Fx Presets
summary: This is a sweetfx preset that is around the same level of quality as a enb without a enb and performance wise it runs about the same as ICBINE 3 i run this on my Mid 2011 mac mini with a Intel HD 3000 graphics card and 4 gb ram
descriptionHtml:
these are sweetfx presets that aims to provide enb like graphics for people like myself who can't run enbs. these are mostly presets i made to play with for myself but thought that a few of you in the community would enjoy and if you like them let me know in the comment section or simply hit the Endorsements Button  


Version 1 is the Dark Fantasy is made for a gritty dark medieval theme 

Version 2 is Dreamlike DreamLike is Bright Colors With pinks and purples Blue nights and Happy days 
 
Version 3 is Dramatic  

Version 4 is Cinematic Sepia is mostly a Sepia effect like the old photos although the nights are strangely bright am 
 

if you want to remove border go into the SweetFX_Settings file and edit this line  #define USE_BORDER            1 //[0 or 1] Border
                                                                                                                      to  #define USE_BORDER            0 //[0 or 1] Bo
ok so i forgot to say this before so for version 1 Dark Fantasy to turn the shaders on and off press the Pause Break button its above the page up button

and for version 2 Dreamlike its the insert button its above the delete button

and for version 3 Dramatic its the insert button its above the delete button







INSTALLATION for Versions 2 3 and 4

Extract to install directory 

that's it then play
